@node intro "Introduction"

	@{b}What is it?@{ub}
Backuper is a program for managin backup disks. It sorts disks, and their contents, and writes the output to ascii files. Backuper is intended to be integrated with a filhandler, for quick and confortable use.

	@{b}Who, How@{ub}
Backuper is written by @{"Albert Bertilsson" link me}, in C.
@endnode


@node install "Installation"

	@{b}Installation@{ub}

	Just copy the executable to a place you like, c: is normal.
@endnode


